Project: NovaCentral (Next.js + Node.js + MongoDB)

Rules:

- Always use axios withCredentials: true
- Auth uses httpOnly cookies (NO localStorage tokens)
- Backend must return { success, msg, data }
- Always validate inputs (amount > 0, required fields)
- Use req.user._id (NOT id)
- Never break existing modules
- Do NOT change unrelated files
- Prevent duplicate transactions (txHash must be unique)
- Use atomic DB operations (avoid race conditions)
- All APIs must handle errors properly (try/catch)
- Never expose sensitive data (private keys, secrets)
- Follow existing project structure
- Keep responses consistent across frontend & backend
